Articles.Content: I uploaded  some mods and since the,my games's water is not displaying anymore,but on my other computer theses mods works just fine

There is absolutely no difference but a mod I installed called near future electrics.but I decided to get rid of all my mods and the problem was solved.
I then tried to reinstall 2 of my mods,waterfall and GEA lite and the problem is still going on

GEA lite
